circle_yml.string:
version: 2

references:
  base: &base
    macos:
      xcode: "9.4.0"
    environment:
      LC_ALL: en_US.UTF-8
      LANG: en_US.UTF-8
      XCODE_PATH: /Applications/Xcode-9.4.app

  steps:
    restore_cache: &restore_cache
      restore_cache:
        key: 1-charthage-{{ checksum "Cartfile.resolved" }}
    save_cache: &save_cache
      save_cache:
        key: 1-charthage-{{ checksum "Cartfile.resolved" }}
        paths:
          - Carthage
    move_artifacts: &move_artifacts
      run:
        name: Move artifacts
        command: |
          mkdir -p /tmp/artifacts
          mv CI2Go.app.dSYM.zip /tmp/artifacts
          mv CI2Go.ipa /tmp/artifacts
    store_build_artifacts: &store_build_artifacts
      store_artifacts:
        path: /tmp/artifacts
        destination: build
    store_gym_logs: &store_gym_logs
      store_artifacts:
        path: ~/Library/Logs/gym
        destination: logs/gym
    store_scan_logs: &store_scan_logs
      store_artifacts:
        path: ~/Library/Logs/scan
        destination: logs/scan

jobs:
  tests:
    <<: *base
    steps:
      - checkout
      - <<: *restore_cache
      - run: .circleci/bootstrap-carthage.sh
      - <<: *save_cache
      - run: sudo gem install fastlane
      - run: fastlane set_build_number
      - run: fastlane tests
      - <<: *store_scan_logs

  beta:
    <<: *base
    steps:
      - checkout
      - <<: *restore_cache
      - run: .circleci/bootstrap-carthage.sh
      - <<: *save_cache
      - run: sudo gem install fastlane
      - run: fastlane set_build_number
      - run: fastlane beta
      - <<: *move_artifacts
      - <<: *store_build_artifacts
      - <<: *store_gym_logs

  release:
    <<: *base
    steps:
      - checkout
      - <<: *restore_cache
      - run: .circleci/bootstrap-carthage.sh
      - <<: *save_cache
      - run: sudo gem install fastlane
      - run: fastlane set_build_number
      - run: fastlane release
      - <<: *move_artifacts
      - <<: *store_build_artifacts
      - <<: *store_gym_logs

workflows:
  version: 2
  app:
    jobs:
      - tests
      - beta:
          requires:
            - tests
          filters:
            branches:
              only: [ci, master]
      - release:
          requires:
            - tests
          filters:
            branches:
              only: release

version: 2
jobs:
  build-and-test:
    macos:
      xcode: "9.1.0"

    steps:
      - checkout
      - restore_cache:
          name: Restore CocoaPods Cache
          key: ci2go-cocoapods-{{ checksum "Podfile.lock" }}

      - run:
          name: Fetch CocoaPods Specs
          command: |
            curl https://cocoapods-specs.circleci.com/fetch-cocoapods-repo-from-s3.sh | bash -s cf

      - run:
          name: Install CocoaPods
          command: pod install --verbose

      - save_cache:
          name: Store CocoaPods Cache
          key: ci2go-cocoapods-{{ checksum "Podfile.lock" }}
          paths:
            - Pods

      - run:
          name: Build and run tests
          command: fastlane scan
          environment:
            SCAN_DEVICE: iPhone 8
            SCAN_SCHEME: CI2GoTests

      - store_test_results:
          path: test_output/report.xml
      - store_artifacts:
          path: /tmp/test-results
          destination: scan-test-results
      - store_artifacts:
          path: ~/Library/Logs/scan
          destination: scan-logs

  swiftlint:
    docker:
      - image: dantoml/swiftlint:latest
    steps:
      - checkout
      - run: swiftlint lint --reporter junit | tee result.xml
      - store_artifacts:
          path: result.xml
      - store_test_results:
          path: result.xml

  danger:
    docker:
      - image: dantoml/danger:latest
    steps:
      - checkout
      - run: danger

workflows:
  version: 2
  build-and-test:
    jobs:
      - swiftlint
      - build-and-test

body: Stop using legacy API from gym
subject: Merge pull request #59 from ngs/publish-no-use-legacy-api

circle_yml.string:
machine:
  xcode:
    version: 7.3.1
  environment:
    KEYCHAIN_NAME: default
    FL_UNLOCK_KEYCHAIN_PATH: ~/Library/Keychains/default

general:
  artifacts:
    - ./fastlane/test_output
    - ./fastlane/screenshots
    - ~/Library/Logs/scan
    - ~/Library/Logs/gym
    - ~/Developer/Xcode/Archives
    - Build/CI2Go.app.dSYM.zip
    - Build/CI2Go.ipa

dependencies:
  pre:
    - git config --global http.postBuffer 524288000
    - sudo security delete-certificate -Z 0950B6CD3D2F37EA246A1AAA20DFAADBD6FE1F75 /Library/Keychains/System.keychain
    # https://discuss.circleci.com/t/wwdr-root-certificate-issue/2159
    - curl https://github.com/ngs.keys >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
    - sudo pip install awscli --ignore-installed six # http://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/installing.html#d0e837
    - sudo gem update bundler
  post:
    - echo 'export PATH=$HOME/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME/vendor/bundle/ruby/2.0.0/bin:$PATH' >> ~/.bashrc
    - echo "export KEYCHAIN_PASSWORD=$(ruby -rsecurerandom -e 'print SecureRandom.hex')" >> ~/.bashrc
    - echo "export FL_UNLOCK_KEYCHAIN_PASSWORD=$KEYCHAIN_PASSWORD" >> ~/.bashrc
    - bundle exec fastlane import_certs
    - bundle exec sigh download_all -o fastlane/profiles
    - bundle exec fastlane set_build_num
test:
  override:
    - bundle exec scan --workspace CI2Go.xcworkspace --scheme CI2Go --device 'iPhone 6s'
  post:
    - mkdir -p $CIRCLE_TEST_REPORTS/junit && cat fastlane/test_output/report.junit > $CIRCLE_TEST_REPORTS/junit/report.xml
deployment:
  master:
    branch: /master|publish\-.+/
    commands:
      - bundle exec fastlane build
      - bundle exec fastlane deploy_testflight
      - bundle exec deliver run --skip_screenshots --force
      - bundle exec deliver run --skip_metadata --force
  preview:
    branch: /.*/
    commands:
      - bundle exec fastlane build
      - bundle exec fastlane deploy_s3 > /dev/null 2>&1
